Example using the BrowserMob Proxy to record HTTP traffic and save off a HTTP Archive.

- Build and install BrowserMob Proxy

Download the source code:

> git clone https://github.com/lightbody/browsermob-proxy

Copy the Maven settings to your home directory, you will need to make
a backup of your old settings.xml.

> cd browsermob-proxy
> cp $(HOME)/.m2/settings.xml $(HOME)/.m2/settings.xml.bak
> cp settings.xml $(HOME)/.m2/settings.xml

Build and install

> mvn
> mvn install

- Open and build the pom.xml file (I used IntelliJ)
